{
  "stem": "19111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 375.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Father David was looking for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at a given moment, we had a door that was leading to the outside-- a secret door, sort of.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was boarded up sort of, but it was made so that we can open up.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we opened it up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he snuck into.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we had a reunion with Father David.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Father David, he brought us a little food as well at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he said he was looking for us for a long time.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Many times, he took walks there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He couldn't make any contact with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his mission was that he saw that whatever-- whatever the future holds in store, he doesn't know, but he's willing to risk it and take me away to-- to his church, because there were a lot of young-- Russian youngsters who were being taught the priesthoods over there.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he would hide me amongst them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when the war ends, you know, and we-- they survived, he would come and-- and-- and take me away.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, that was a very, very genuine effort on his part.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my mother said to him that we're gonna think about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We're gonna come to a conclusion, and that next time he'll pass by, we'll let him know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He was-- also had tears in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And my father-- [INAUDIBLE] my father and my mother discussing this matter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they-- they decided not to do it, because they were afraid that the children that I would be exposed to-- the rest of them may expose me, and I'll be caught and I'll be killed right on the spot by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that's why I did not go into the church at the time.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
